            "type": "rich_text_section",
            "elements": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "I would like to reiterate the points made here that discusses the reasons textual or visual languages are better for different domains:\n\n"
              },
              {
                "type": "link",
                "url": "https://futureofcoding.slack.com/archives/C5T9GPWFL/p1599034947086700?thread_ts=1598907017.049900&cid=C5T9GPWFL"
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "\n\nWithin this analytically framework, it seems obvious that LabVIEW takes the better approach for the task toward which it is oriented, but would feel awkward for some differently shaped problem domains."
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      }
